Kita harus ke Rumah sakit.
Cepat!

62
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:09,100
Makanlah sedikit, Bu.

63
00:08:18,100 --> 00:08:20,700
Berat badanmu menyusut.

64
00:08:21,300 --> 00:08:24,078
Kuharap kau mampu makan bubur.

65
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:26,900
Hanya sup saja tak cukup untukmu.

66
00:08:35,700 --> 00:08:38,100
Ceyda. Apakah kau lapar, sayang?

67
