"Tunggu saja, mungkin mereda"

125
00:13:59,300 --> 00:14:01,100
"Air ketubanku pecah!"

126
00:14:01,100 --> 00:14:03,600
"Aku sudah mau melahirkan!"

127
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:10,011
"Saraf matanya terluka parah."

128
00:14:10,036 --> 00:14:12,100
"Sayang sekali,
bayi Anda tak akan dapat melihat."

129
