Sudah berakhir!

159
00:17:44,000 --> 00:17:45,900
"Jangan hubungi aku lagi!"

160
00:17:47,600 --> 00:17:49,600
Kau laki-laki brengsek!

161
00:17:49,600 --> 00:17:51,900
Terimalah nanti balasannya!

162
00:18:23,500 --> 00:18:25,100
Ceyda?

163
